  <h2>7. Web Beacons &amp; Local Storage</h2>
  <p>
    In addition to cookies, we use:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> To store lightweight data (like your theme preference) locally on your browser. This data is not sent to our server with every request.</li>
    <li><strong>Web Beacons (Pixels):</strong> Small invisible images in our emails to track if you opened them (only applicable if you have opted into our Newsletter).</li>
  </ul>

